Dialogue: 0,1:03:04.96,1:03:05.61,DefaultSingle-J,,0,0,0,,	{\a6\fscx90\fscy90}	7
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.08,1:03:06.65,DefaultSingle-J,,0,0,0,,	{\a6\fscx90\fscy90}	6
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.10,1:03:07.71,DefaultSingle-J,,0,0,0,,	{\a6\fscx90\fscy90}	5
Dialogue: 0,1:03:08.20,1:03:08.80,DefaultSingle-J,,0,0,0,,	{\a6\fscx90\fscy90}	4
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.24,1:03:09.86,DefaultSingle-J,,0,0,0,,	{\a6\fscx90\fscy90}	3
